name: TimeRange

values.name: difference
values.comment: Get the `Time` difference between the start and end time in the time range.

values.name: end
values.comment: Get the end time for the range.

values.name: fromStartAndEnd
values.comment: Construct a time range from start and end times.

values.name: isContainedWithin
values.comment: Allows you to find out if a given `Time` is contained within a `TimeRange`.

values.name: overlaps
values.comment: Allows you to find out if two `TimeRange`s overlap.

values.name: start
values.comment: Get the start time for the range.
